FROM --platform=$BUILDPLATFORM golang:1.26.4-alpine3.23@sha256:f23e8b227fb4493eabe03bede4d5a32d04092da71962f1fb79b5f7d1e6c2a17f AS builder

WORKDIR /app

COPY . .

RUN go build -o /app/out/ /app/cmd/ratify-gatekeeper-provider

FROM gcr.io/distroless/static:nonroot@sha256:e8a4044e0b4ae4257efa45fc026c0bc30ad320d43bd4c1a7d5271bd241e386d0

WORKDIR /app

COPY --from=builder /app/out/ratify-gatekeeper-provider ./

EXPOSE 6001

USER 65532:65532

ENTRYPOINT ["/app/ratify-gatekeeper-provider"]
